        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion - The Final Lucira Tip",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Your engagement ring tells a story and your photos should too. With simple adjustments in light, angles, hand poses, and editing, you can capture engagement ring photos that show the true sparkle, emotion and beauty of your ring.</p><p>Whether you love candid moments, close up ring photography, or sweet engagement ring couple photos, these tips help every picture feel natural, glowing, and full of life. Because your ring deserves to shine the way it does in real life.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion"
          }
        }
